== Itegeko rihana ikoreshwa ry' amasashi na parasiki ==
Mu mwaka wa 2008, Leta y’u Rwanda yasohoye itegeko ribuza ikorwa, itumizwa, ikoreshwa n’icuruzwa ry’amasashi akoze muri parasitiki.

Iri tegeko rinagena n’ibihano ku warirezeho birimo igifungo kiva ku mezi atandatu kugeza ku mwaka n’ihazabu iva ku bihumbi 100 kugera ku bihumbi 500 Frw cyangwa kimwe muri byo ku bakora cyangwa abakoresha aya masashi.

Ugurisha  aya masashi we ahanishwa kuva ku ihazabu y’ibihumbi 10 kugera ku bihumbi 300 Frw, naho umuntu wese utabyemerewe ukoresha aya masashi  ahanishwa ihazabu iri hagati y’ibihumbi 5 n’ibihumbi 100<ref>Amashashi REMA yayahagurukiye…Uyafatanywe aracibwa agera kuri 300 000 Frw – UMUSEKE</ref>

== Ikoreshwa ry'amashashi na parasiki  byangiza ibidukikije ==
Nyuma yikorwa ry'ubushakakashatsi ku bidukikije reta y'uRwanda ibicishije mu Ikigo cy’ igihugu cyo kurengera ibidukikije REMA  bagarageje muri zimwe mu ngaruka mbi ziterwa n'ikoreshwa ry' amashashi na pulastiki zikurikira :<ref>Ikindi gikorwa cyo kurwanya ikoreshwa ry’amashashi - IGIHE.com</ref>

* Amashashi na parasiki bigira ingaruka mbi kubidukikije harimo gutuma amazi y’imvura atabasha gucengera mu butaka n’umusaruro w’ubuhinzi ukagabanuka.
* Amashashi  na parasiki  arekura imyuka ihumanya igihe atwitswe cyangwa akoreshejwe mu gupfundikira ibiryo biri ku ziko.
* Amashashi na parasiki biteza umwanda ku bidukije ndetse no mu nzuzi n'imigezi kuko bitabora .
* Amashashi na purasiki byangiza inzira z' amazi bikaba byateza isuru .
* Amashashi na parsiki byangiza urusobe rw'ibinyabuzima byo mu mazi <ref>Guca amashashi byagabanyije umwanda muri Kigali - Kigali Today</ref>.

